<text>The [[Bram Stoker Award]] for First Novel is an award presented by the Horror Writers Association (HWA) for &quot;superior achievement&quot; in horror writing for an author&#x27;s first horror novel.

==Winners and nominees==


== References ==</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q848943" start="4" end="41" title="Bram Stoker Award for Best First Novel" label="[[Bram Stoker Award]] for First Novel"/>
<link wikidata="Q5905197" start="71" end="97" title="Horror Writers Association" label="Horror Writers Association"/>
<link wikidata="Q16575965" start="144" end="158" title="Horror fiction" label="horror writing"/>
