*Canon
*Dalsa (formerly part of Philips)
*Foveon
*Fujifilm, designers of the Super CCD
*Matsushita
*Nikon (designs, but as of 2006 does not yet fabricate)
*Sony
*Samsung Digital Imaging, part of Samsung Corporation
*Toshiba

