<doc id="425665" wikidata="Q3910468" url="?curid=425665" title="Bram Stoker Award for Best Work for Young Readers">
<text>The [[Bram Stoker Award]] for Best Work for Young Readers is a discontinued award presented by the Horror Writers Association (HWA) for &quot;superior achievement&quot; in horror writing for young readers.

==Winners and nominees==
Nominees are listed below the winner(s) for each year.


