<doc id="425719" wikidata="Q3910466" url="?curid=425719" title="Bram Stoker Award for Best Illustrated Narrative">
<text>The [[Bram Stoker Award]] for Best Illustrated Narrative is an award presented by the Horror Writers Association (HWA) for &quot;superior achievement&quot; in horror writing for comic books.

== Honorees ==
Nominees are listed below the winner(s) for each year.

